body_html: The dot files wouldn't help a lot, but if you can dump a SessionModule proto (--xla_dump_computations_to=/tmp/foo, possibly passing the flag via the TF_XLA_FLAGS envvar), that is probably enough for us to reproduce. You'd want to dump this from TF built at or near to HEAD, as that format changes, and our tools can't necessarily go back.
